data.description: Investment opportunity for seasoned investors and house hackers alike. One year Home Warranty offered along with current rents of $950 for unit 1 and $1,150 for unit 2, this income-generating gem is ready to cash flow. Both tenants have been meticulously screened, ensuring a hassle-free experience from day one.Step inside this updated home and be greeted by a charming common sunroom, perfect for relaxation or socializing. Recent renovations include fresh paint and new flooring, creating a modern and inviting atmosphere for tenants. The fenced-in yard provides privacy and security, making it an attractive feature for tenants. Furthermore, the newer utilities ensure low maintenance costs and peace of mind for the savvy investor.Notably, this property easily meets the rigorous standards set by FHA and VA.
